# Clean seed repo exclusions
*.md
!src/project_remedy/behavioral_proxies/**/prompts/
!src/project_remedy/behavioral_proxies/**/prompts/*.md
!src/project_remedy/quality_judges/**/prompts/
!src/project_remedy/quality_judges/**/prompts/*.md
docs/
doc/
knowledge-base/
knowledge_base/
*knowledge-base*/
tests/
test/
__tests__/
test_*.py
*_test.py
*.test.*
*.spec.*
!README.md
!src/**/*.py
!backend/**/*.py
!tools/**/*.py

# Screenshots / demo recordings — not part of source
screenshots/

# Graphify knowledge-graph output (generated, ~36MB) — not source
graphify-out/

# Committed unit tests (exception to the local-only tests/ policy above).
# Keep tests/ ignored (heavy corpus/integration stays local) but commit only
# tests/unit/*.py. Order matters — these are last-match-wins over the tests/
# and test_*.py patterns above. Negating *.py only (not tests/unit/**) keeps
# __pycache__/*.pyc out. Verify with: git check-ignore -v tests/unit/<f>.py
!tests/
tests/*
!tests/unit/
!tests/unit/*.py
